an class=title>   Re: Francine Rivers</span><hr size=1> Redeeming Love is my favourite book in the entire world. <br>
<br>
It's the most amazing love story...but it's also about the enduring love God has for us. Francine Rivers has likened it to the 'story inside of her that just needed to be written'. It's the most amazing book...I challenge anyone to read it and not be changed. <br>
<br>
Basically, for all of you that want to know, it's the story of a prostitute, Angel. Sold into the sex industry at 8, she's lived a life of hate and bitterness until one man comes and changes it all. The man that she hates.... <p><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://www.planetwisdom.com/myspace/lace//salt1.gif" style="border:0;"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--><!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="color:99cccc;font-family:Dom Casual BT;font-size:medium;">Seasoned with grace, Lacey</span><!--EZCODE FONT END--><br>
